{"tid":1354783,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急呼籲］橙色撤離警告","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:43:43.000Z","uid":246671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f89903a8758df9c56a3645f415716003102edc94","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">橙色撤離警告</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有見及香港<span style=\"color: red;\">官商鄉黑</span>勾結嚴重，我們將於7月27日發起<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復元朗，鏟除警黑，光復香港，時代革命</span></span>大遊行，期間呼籲示威人士保持克制確保社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n有見及7月21日期間普通市民受到<span style=\"color: red;\">鄉黑暴打</span>，民情正處於沸點，遊行期間部分遊行人士會作出<span style=\"color: red;\">較激進</span>行為<br />\n<br />\n故此在此呼籲各涉案圍村勢力盡快<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤離村中老幼</span></span>，以免受到不必要的驚嚇</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*橙色為警方於中環開槍的警告色，請參考此合理武力標準"},{"pid":"ee20d2710330d947a9bda2b470b4c7481187be83","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f15fd238446acae44740a909f2841632be6d51c5","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"155e4384ebce18c6c37f6de0422a173e98a06941","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35780e86765455a35f892fbf01499eea8abb9d5f","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c40f984082ad1500fcd4ed6fb6324829f2b4e961","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a1ac1494b4dc630e3073fd0404f61fd08027243","tid":1354783,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s